Page_0: "It has become clear to me that Lady Antonette is merely trying to delay my purchase...

I suspect that Warden Nightfall will attempt some operation during my absence. Quietly take the men downstairs and return to my manor. Once you are there, wake every guard and search every room until you are sure that it is secure. Tomorrow we will seize and execute every known agent of Nightfall found within my territory. I have simply had enough of his pretensions to power.

~L.W.Raputo"